Askaway is your new tool to ask anyone any question behind the veil of anonymity.

Flow :

You provide 
- The question
- Any contact handler like thier
-- Twitter pseudonim
-- Facebook id
-- Email
-- Phone number

The contact replies and chooses to send their answer to either 
- their public profile page
- just to the person asking
- no one and block you forever and the eternity

Answers can also be conditioned on the asker revealing their identity.

